      <title>阈值自控意识</title>
      <link>https://yxzi.xyz/Sub/Blog/mynote/2-%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9/%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E8%83%BD%E8%B5%9A%E9%92%B1%E5%90%97/</link>
